*Teltoli grunts as she gets up* "I don't think so, Predac-" *She stops as Ramhorn fights the two bots, appearing to flash out of nowhere. It was kinda weird, a rhino bot being so fast at fighting. She tries to stop the flow of mech-fluid out of her stomach as she watches the fight, hoping Ramhorn doesn't get seriously hurt for her..*

------Original Message------
From: KSLawdogg@...
To: nbwrpg@egroups.com
Sent: May 10, 2000 5:22:19 AM GMT
Subject: Re: Neo Beast Wars


(Could someone post damage for the Ark, I'm interested in how much damage my 
attacks did, I'd prefer Iron Raptor to do it.)
Dark One/Injector/Manterror/Ramhorn:


::Injector chuckled, firing off three more stinger missiles at the Ark::
::Turning to Teltoli:: "Ah, poor little Maximal.  Time to die!"

::Manterror stepped forward::
"Nothing withstands the Manterror!"

"Picking on defenseless female robots, you guys are just pathetic." (Ramhorn 
said, slamming the but of laser pistol onto the back of Injector's head, 
sending the lionfish/hornet collapsing to the ground with a small crack on 
the back of his oddly shaped head::

"Coward, to face the Manterror is to face defeat!"
::Manterror fired off an ion disk, Ramhorn rolling to the left, firing a bolt 
from his laser pistol, Manterror yelling in pain, Ramhorn leaping forward and 
uppercutting the praying mantis::

::Ramhorn punched Manterror once, then a knee to stomach::

"Ugh!  Ufgh!" (Manterror swiped his claws, slicing the side of Ramhorn head, 
then kicking the rhino in the left knee, with a fierce uppercut ripping apart 
one of Ramhorn's optics::

::Ramhorn threw his laser pistol, the barrel hitting Manterror in the middle 
of the head.  As the Predacon 'grabbed' his forehead in pain, Ramhorn leaped 
forward, tackling him to the ground and punching him in the face a few times, 
Manterror kneeing him in the stomach, gripping him and slamming him to the 
side into the ground::
